1.5-Minute Reservation Allows users to reserve a bike 5 minutes in advance to ensure a ride is waiting for them upon arrival.

2.Dublin Weather & News Provides real-time weather updates and relevant local news to help users decide if it is a good day for cycling.

3.Station Information Displays precise station locations and a list of available services at each dock on an interactive map.

4.Real-Time Bike Availability Shows the live count of available bikes and empty stands at every station to prevent "no-bike" or "no-dock" frustrations.

5.Rental Tracking & History Monitors the duration of the current ride to track costs and provides a detailed history of all past rentals.

6.Subscriptions & Top-Ups Enables users to manage various plans (Daily, Monthly, or Annual) or add credit to their account for single-use trips.

7.Bike Damage Reporting A reporting tool for users to flag broken bikes; successful reports earn "Reward Points" that can be redeemed for free cycling time.
